com.sudoplay.axion.spec.tag

Class TagList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sudoplay.axion.tag.Tag
      • com.sudoplay.axion.tag.ContainerTag
        • com.sudoplay.axion.spec.tag.TagList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Tag>

    public class TagList
extends ContainerTag
    Author:
    Jason Taylor
    Tag Type:
    9
    Tag Name:
    TAG_List
    Tag Payload:
    * TAG_Byte tagId
    * TAG_Int length
    * A sequential list of Tags (not Named Tags), of type typeId. The length of this array is length Tags.
    Note:
    All tags share the same type.
